---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Features - letsorder"
  description="Explore the powerful features of letsorder, designed to streamline your restaurant management and enhance the customer experience."
>
  <!-- Key Features for Restaurants -->
  <section id="features" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Everything You Need to Manage Your Restaurant
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Powerful tools designed specifically for restaurant managers to streamline operations and enhance customer experience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Menu Management</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Create and organize menu sections and items with ease. Update prices, descriptions, and availability in real-time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v1m6 11h2m-6 0h-2v4m0-11v3m0 0h.01M12 12h4.01M16 20h4M4 12h4m12 0h.01M5 8h2a1 1 0 001-1V6a1 1 0 00-1-1H5a1 1 0 00-1 1v1a1 1 0 001 1z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">QR Code Generation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Generate unique QR codes for each table or room. Customers scan to access your menu instantly - no app downloads required.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Order Management</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            View all orders in real-time. Track which table placed each order and manage your kitchen workflow efficiently.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Multi-Manager Support</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Invite multiple managers with customizable permissions. Super admin controls who can manage menus and view orders.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Secure & Reliable</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Built with security in mind. Continuous database backups and monitoring ensure your data is always safe and accessible.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Fast & Simple</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            No complex setup required. Get your restaurant online in minutes, not hours. Simple interface that anyone can use.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
